<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TrustLoop - Customer Experience Resolution Engine</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --color-primary: #0F766E;
      --color-primary-dark: #0D5D56;
      --color-primary-light: #14B8A6;
    }

    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0F766E 0%, #1E293B 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .nav {
      padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .nav-brand {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 2rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover {
      color: white;
    }

    .hero {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-content {
      max-width: 700px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .hero p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 0.875rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }

    .btn-white {
      background: white;
      color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .btn-white:hover {
      background: #F8FAFC;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-outline {
      background: transparent;
      color: white;
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    }

    .btn-outline:hover {
      border-color: white;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    .features {
      background: white;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }

    .features-container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .features h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #1E293B;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
    }

    .feature-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0.75rem;
      background: #F8FAFC;
    }

    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      color: #1E293B;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .feature-card p {
      color: #64748B;
      font-size: 0.9375rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .footer {
      background: #1E293B;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);
      font-size: 0.875rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
      .hero p { font-size: 1rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav class="nav">
    <a href="/" class="nav-brand">TrustLoop</a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
      <a href="/auth/register">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Turn Every Experience Into Trust</h1>
      <p>
        TrustLoop helps you understand customer sentiment and resolve issues before they become public reviews.
        FTC-compliant, customer-first approach.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/auth/register" class="btn btn-white">Get Started Free</a>
        <a href="/auth/login" class="btn btn-outline">Sign In</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <div class="features-container">
      <h2>Why TrustLoop?</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Binary Sentiment</h3>
          <p>Simple "Great!" or "I had an issue" feedback. No confusing star ratings. Clear signals for action.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Resolution First</h3>
          <p>Address concerns directly with customers. Fix issues before they become negative reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>FTC Compliant</h3>
          <p>Google review links are always visible. No gating, no blocking. Just honest customer choice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Smart Analytics</h3>
          <p>Track customer journeys, sentiment trends, and resolution success. Make data-driven decisions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Easy Integration</h3>
          <p>Generate unique links for each customer. Share via email, SMS, or QR code. Simple and effective.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <h3>Privacy Focused</h3>
          <p>Your customer data stays yours. No third-party sharing. Built with privacy in mind.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">
    <p>TrustLoop - Customer Experience Resolution Engine</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
